description: Tonal coloring reigns in the controlled chaos of texture, proportion and dimension defining Nike's more-is-more OverBreak sneaker. It sits on springy Nike React foam that propels the sneakerhead momentum with every step, with layered Swooshes anchoring the sides and an opaque toe cap clearly enjoying the attention of the chunky-spattered sole.
features: Cushioning: absorbs impact and distributes weight for consistent, buoyant comfort under each step
Nike React foam sole turns every step into springy returned energy
Synthetic and textile upper/textile and synthetic lining/rubber and synthetic sole
sellingStatement: Tonal coloring reigns in the controlled chaos of texture, proportion and dimension defining Nike's more-is-more OverBreak sneaker.

Modules.liveText:
Free shipping. Free returns. All the time. Purchases made online can also be returned or exchanged at any Nordstrom store, free of charge. Read more about our shipping & returns policies.

  • Customized items are final sale so they can’t be returned.
  • Designer items can only be returned if they are in the same condition as purchased and with all tags attached.
